.. _development-quickstart:

========================
 Development quickstart
========================

Source Code
===========

NIPYPE uses sourceforge_ for our code hosting.  For immediate access to
the source code, see the `nipy sourceforge`_ site.

Please see the `NIPY developer resources`_ site.

.. _trunk_download:

Checking out the latest version
===============================

To check out the latest version of nipy you need subversion_ ::

    svn co https://nipy.svn.sourceforge.net/svnroot/nipy/nipype/trunk/ nipype

Unpack the tarball and change into the source directory.  Once in the
source directory, you can build the nipype using::

    python setup.py install

